| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0185 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6d46084c-29ae-5f41-8045-6a7b6e179d9d"
